Sentencas: A new cathode material fabricated by solid state reaction method was reported.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and electrochemical properties of SmVO4 cathode materials for low temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The SmVO4 powder was obtained by firing the mixture of Sm2O3 and V2O5 powders in the temperature range of 700 - 1200 degrees C.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and electrochemical properties of SmVO4 cathode materials for low temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: Its structure was identified by X-ray diffraction method and the electrochemical properties of SmVO4 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) were investigated in single unit cell at the temperature ranged from 450 - 550 degrees C.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and electrochemical properties of SmVO4 cathode materials for low temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The results of the single fuel cell unit show that the maximum current densities are 641, 797, 688 mA center dot cm(-2) and the maximum power output are 165, 268, 303 mW center dot cm(-2) and the open circuit voltage are 1.04, 0.96, 0.92 V at 450, 500 and 550 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and electrochemical properties of SmVO4 cathode materials for low temperature SOFCs
